com.quartzy.engine.math

Class Vector3f

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.quartzy.engine.math.Vector3f

  • public class Vector3f
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a (x,y,z)-Vector. GLSL equivalent to vec3.
